Rating: 3
I thought this recipe easy and very good. My husband, who usually will ONLY eat dark meat, actually liked it. In fact, he ate the leftovers for lunch the next day. I would use a little extra prosciutto for more flavor but the caper sauce was perfect. Will definitely make again.

